"of (rule, initial, k) — author intention does not enter." . cr
cr
"Iteration 1: nodes=3,   edges=3   (3^1)" . cr
"Iteration 2: nodes=6,   edges=9   (3^2)" . cr
"Iteration 3: nodes=15,  edges=27  (3^3)" . cr
"Iteration 4: nodes=42,  edges=81  (3^4)" . cr
cr
