"substrate-monism sense — output is determined by substrate dynamics," . cr
"not author intention." . cr
cr
"What this addresses: the 'Pilot D cosmogenesis is hand-coded'" . cr
"critique.  This demo's 81 edges at k=4 are NOT a target the author" . cr
"selected; they are the unique value the substrate produces." . cr
cr
